data.description: Spacious Madison home on over half an acre! This functional floorplan offers plenty of living space for your entire family both inside and out. Comfortably host holiday gatherings in the formal dining room at the front of the home that flows effortlessly into the eat-in kitchen so your home chef never has to miss a moment. A large open patio in the oversized privacy fenced backyard extends your living space outdoors with plenty of room for gameday barbeques while the sunroom with jacuzzi provides a comfortable indoor/outdoor space. Complete with an attached two-car garage, rear-entry shop, and home office, this one won’t last long! Schedule your showing today before it’s too late!
